    <h3>Three descriptions of the same break</h3>

    <p>
      A temporal graph journey breaks when timing fails to compose.
      A P-frame chain breaks when a reference is lost.
      A sheaf's local sections fail to extend globally when exactness fails.
      Different triggers, same structural pattern: downstream validity depends
      on every earlier link.
    </p>

